                      or long reads only assembly. It accepts Illumina, ONT and
                      Pacbio data.

                      It uses Unicycler, Flye, Canu or Spades to assemble reads.
                      And uses Nanopolish, VariantCaller or Pilon to polish assemblies.

*/

